{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c6f69e53a8","title":"关于相机透露毛泽东准备辞去国家主席职务给审乡的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b50a8df84d","index":0,"year":1958,"month":7,"day":31,"articleId":"c6f69e53a8"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"36690b0ce3","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"宜乡，当时任中国驻英国大使馆代办。"},{"id":"27dc85e389","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。朱，指朱德。林，指林彪，当时任中共中央副主席。陈，指陈云，当时任中共中央副主席。邓，指邓小平，当时任中共中央总书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"46051f8a3d","type":"title","text":"关于相机透露毛泽东准备辞去国家主席职务给乡的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8"},{"id":"36690b0ce3","type":"paragraph","text":"发驻英便馆审乡同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8"},{"id":"27dc85e389","type":"paragraph","text":"六月二十日你给外交部的电报我看了。所传辞职事是真正的。我决心辞去国家主席一职，中央及省市同志都认为有利，正向地县区乡干部通知，并展开辩论，以免临时显得突然。国内民主党派已通知并酯酿一年多了。在华外人，如苏新使节及前印度大使尼赫售等亦已谈过。请你经过新华社记者在伦敦新闻记者中相机陆续放出一点空气。要是非正式的，以闲谈方式出之。经过英共记者，或更好些。逐步使人们不当作谣言，而当作事实。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8"},{"id":"58e265fe8b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8"},{"id":"e9d656a308","type":"paragraph","text":"七月三十一日刘、周、朱、林、陈、邓阅发。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8"}],"page":{"id":"ed775075b7","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c6f69e53a8","start":511,"end":512}}}},"__N_SSG":true}